                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8027" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0221</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1037 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">兰心蕙质：兰卫医学的社会责任战略与效益均衡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">LAN Xin Hui Quality: the social responsibility strategy and benefit balance of LAN Wei Medical</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙红梅，陈依然，陈艺菲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海兰卫医学检验所股份有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">管理战略；社会责任；经济效益；效益均衡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Management strategy, social responsibility, economic benefits, benefits balance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着全球经济的发展和人们对社会可持续发展的重视，企业社会责任和战略管理之间的交叉融合已成为研究的热点。因此，研究如何履行社会责任并获得可持续的竞争优势以提升财务绩效已成为企业关注的焦点。本案例以医学检验与病理诊断为主要服务的上市公司-上海兰卫医学检验所有限公司为研究对象，以战略性社会责任、利益相关者理论为基础，描述兰卫医学长期致力公益的社会责任战略与企业经济效益发生矛盾与均衡决策的过程。公司董事长曾伟雄先生不忘以人为本的初衷，追求履责和发展共生，不断引领企业突破矛盾瓶颈，实现了社会责任与效益的均衡。本案例帮助学生理解企业如何将社会责任战略融合到经营业务中，通过具体案例企业如何平衡财务绩效和社会责任的冲突点，了解企业如何利用运筹社会责任战略获得长期的效益发展，加深学生对企业履行社会责任的认同感，增强学生可持续发展的理念。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the development of global economy and people&#39;s emphasis on sustainable social development, the cross-fertilization between corporate social responsibility and strategic management has become a hot research topic. Therefore, research on how to fulfill social responsibility and gain sustainable competitive advantage to enhance financial performance has become the focus of corporate attention. This case takes Shanghai Lanwei Medical Laboratory Co., Ltd, a listed company which mainly provides medical testing and pathology diagnosis services, as the research object, and describes the process of conflict and balanced decision-making between the social responsibility strategy of Lanwei Medical&#39;s long-term commitment to public welfare and the economic benefits of the enterprise based on the theories of strategic social responsibility and stakeholder. The chairman of the company, Mr.Zeng, never forgets the original intention of putting people first, pursues the symbiosis of responsibility and development, and constantly leads the company to break through the bottleneck of contradiction and achieve the balance between social responsibility and benefits. This case helps students to understand how enterprises integrate social responsibility strategy into their business operations, how to balance the conflict between financial performance and social responsibility through specific cases, how to understand how enterprises utilize the operation of the social responsibility strategy to obtain long-term benefits and development, to deepen the students&#39; identification with the fulfillment of social responsibility by enterprises, and to enhance the students&#39; concept of sustainable development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业伦理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略社会责任理论；社会责任生态理论；利益相关者理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
